div.p:
ohhh yesss—let’s make “HK” dance on your README! 🕺💙
GitHub README can’t run JS, but an animated SVG works perfectly. Here’s a drop-in file that makes “HK” orbit in a circle, bob up/down, and tilt like it’s grooving.
div.h3: 1) Save this as assets/hk-dance.svg in your profile repo (Harihk082005/Harihk082005)

li.p: You can tweak the color by changing fill="#0E75B6" to your green/brand color.
Make it faster/slower by changing dur="8s" (orbit) or dur="1.2s" (bounce/tilt).
Want it bigger? Increase the width/height.

div.p: Want a version that moves in a figure-8 or spirals for a few seconds before looping? Say the word and I’ll drop alternate SVGs. 💃✨
